{Hopscotch.                            
{                                      
 Hopscotch is an old game.You chalk a  
 grid on the ground and write numbers  
 from 1 to 10 in the squares. Then you 
 throw a stone in to the grid and hop  
 up the grid missing the number that   
 your stone has landed on. When you get
 to the top of the grid you turn round 
 and hop back to the start picking up  
 your stone on the way. The winner of  
 the game is the person who collects   
 all the numbers 1 to 10 in order      
 first.                                
                                       
                                       
